r11352 | havoc | 2011-09-15 12:12:19 -0700 (Thu, 15 Sep 2011) | 7 lines
Changed paths:
   M /trunk/darkplaces/cd_shared.c
   M /trunk/darkplaces/gl_textures.c
   M /trunk/darkplaces/snd_main.c
