r11344 | vortex | 2011-09-12 09:53:12 -0700 (Mon, 12 Sep 2011) | 1 line
Changed paths:
   M /trunk/darkplaces/csprogs.c
   M /trunk/darkplaces/csprogs.h
   M /trunk/darkplaces/dpdefs/csprogsdefs.qc
