r10109 | havoc | 2010-05-01 09:48:33 -0700 (Sat, 01 May 2010) | 7 lines
Changed paths:
   M /trunk/darkplaces/cl_particles.c
   M /trunk/darkplaces/cl_screen.c
   M /trunk/darkplaces/client.h
   M /trunk/darkplaces/clvm_cmds.c
