r8254 | havoc | 2008-04-12 02:22:04 -0700 (Sat, 12 Apr 2008) | 6 lines
Changed paths:
   M /trunk/darkplaces/gl_backend.c

added gl_workaround_mac_texmatrix cvar to allow some testing to be done
on the osx GLSL texmatrix bug
