r8243 | havoc | 2008-04-06 10:48:33 -0700 (Sun, 06 Apr 2008) | 3 lines
Changed paths:
   M /trunk/darkplaces/gl_backend.c

fix div0's GL_BuildOrtho which break compilation on Windows
