r7350 | havoc | 2007-05-23 10:15:21 -0700 (Wed, 23 May 2007) | 3 lines
Changed paths:
   M /trunk/darkplaces/cl_main.c

remove stupid int casts of pitch/yaw in beam code, yet another instance
