------------------------------------------------------------------------
r6746 | havoc | 2007-01-23 20:15:45 -0800 (Tue, 23 Jan 2007) | 4 lines
Changed paths:
   M /trunk/darkplaces/clvm_cmds.c
   M /trunk/darkplaces/csprogs.c
   M /trunk/darkplaces/mvm_cmds.c
   M /trunk/darkplaces/progs.h
