   M /trunk/darkplaces/snd_dma.c
   M /trunk/darkplaces/snd_ogg.c
   M /trunk/darkplaces/snd_wav.c
   M /trunk/darkplaces/sound.h

"soundlist" now tells you if a sound is streamed and whether it is mono or stereo

