r3038 | havoc | 2003-05-25 15:46:31 -0700 (Sun, 25 May 2003) | 6 lines
Changed paths:
   M /trunk/darkplaces/cl_main.c
   M /trunk/darkplaces/net.h
   M /trunk/darkplaces/net_dgrm.c
