r2432 | havoc | 2002-09-24 05:16:28 -0700 (Tue, 24 Sep 2002) | 8 lines
Changed paths:
   M /trunk/darkplaces/common.c
   M /trunk/darkplaces/common.h
   M /trunk/darkplaces/darkplaces.dsp
   M /trunk/darkplaces/host.c
