r141 | lordhavoc | 2001-01-29 00:14:37 -0800 (Mon, 29 Jan 2001) | 2 lines
Changed paths:
   M /trunk/darkplaces/common.c
   M /trunk/darkplaces/common.h
   M /trunk/darkplaces/fractalnoise.c
